{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id7877e20b-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s695p"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"695p"},"text":"§ 695p.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Regulation of waters to maintain sump levels","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In carrying out the obligations of the United States under any migratory bird treaty, the Migratory Bird Treaty Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/40/755"},"text":"40 Stat. 755","children":[],"tail":"), as amended ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s703"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 703","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], or the Migratory Bird Conservation Act ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/45/1222"},"text":"45 Stat. 1222","children":[],"tail":"), as amended ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s715"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 715","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], waters under the control of the Secretary of the Interior shall be regulated, subject to valid existing rights, to maintain sump levels in the Tule Lake National Wildlife Refuge at levels established by regulations issued by the Secretary pursuant to the contract between the United States and the Tulelake Irrigation District, dated "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1956-09-10"},"text":"September 10, 1956","children":[],"tail":", or any amendment thereof. Such regulations shall accommodate to the maximum extent practicable waterfowl management needs."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id7877e20c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/567/s6"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–567, § 6","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1964-09-02"},"text":"Sept. 2, 1964","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/78/851"},"text":"78 Stat. 851","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id7877e20d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id7877e20e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id7877e20f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Migratory Bird Treaty Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/40/755"},"text":"40 Stat. 755","children":[],"tail":"), referred to in text, is "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1918-07-03/ch128"},"text":"act July 3, 1918, ch. 128","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/40/755"},"text":"40 Stat. 755","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to subchapter II of chapter 7 (§ 703 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s710"},"text":"section 710 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Migratory Bird Conservation Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/45/1222"},"text":"45 Stat. 1222","children":[],"tail":"), as amended, referred to in text, is "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1929-02-18/ch257"},"text":"act Feb. 18, 1929, ch. 257","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/45/1222"},"text":"45 Stat. 1222","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to subchapter III (§ 715 et seq.) of chapter 7 of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s715"},"text":"section 715 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
